dcterms:description: The Foursquare dataset includes users' check-in histories in cities such as New York, Los Angeles, and Chicago, providing a rich source of historical check-in data for developing Point-of-Interest (POI) recommendation systems.
dcterms:title: Foursquare

dcterms:creator: X. Liu
Y. Liu
K. Aberer
C. Miao
dcterms:description: The Weeplace dataset consists of users' check-in histories in various cities, similar to Foursquare, and is used for personalized point-of-interest recommendation by analyzing users' preference transitions.
dcterms:title: Weeplace
